rows.label: qst103606_msg0001
rows.name:
Brionac...
I thought by defeating their leaders
we had weakened them sufficiently...

rows.label: qst103606_msg0002
rows.name: Yet they seem to be going strong, still.

rows.label: qst103606_msg0003
rows.name:
It appears we have no recourse but to
deploy to the Brionac Occupied Zone
and put them down decisively.

rows.label: qst103606_msg0004
rows.name:
As you say.
This threat to the Empire
cannot be left to fester...
